# TXTNodalExporter translations 2 ux uy
# TXTNodalExporter pressure 1 pressure
## export data in every nodes
# TXTNodalExporter translations 2 ux uy
# TXTNodalExporter pressure 1 pressure
## export data in gaus points
# TXTGaussPointExporter damage 6 x y damage cumSlip slip multip
## displacement gauge uy x1coord y1coord x2coord y2coord 
DisplacementGauge LD displY uy 0.5e0 0.5e0 2e0 1e0
DisplacementGauge LD displX ux 0.5e0 0.5e0 2e0 1e0
## ForceGauge file_name gauge_name which_force how_many node_ids
ForceGauge LD loadY fy 1 1
ForceGauge LD loadX fx 1 1
## export VTK file
VTKElementExporter elems 0
